	<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Portal storm</h1>
	
	<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
		<div id="siteSub" class="noprint">From The Cataclysm: Dark Days Ahead Wiki</div>
		<div id="contentSub"><div class="mw-revision"><div id="mw-revision-info">Revision as of 10:54, 27 September 2022 by <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=User:Mrstickman1997&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new mw-userlink" title="User:Mrstickman1997 (page does not exist)"><bdi>Mrstickman1997</bdi></a> <span class="mw-usertoollinks">(<a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/User_talk:Mrstickman1997" class="mw-usertoollinks-talk" title="User talk:Mrstickman1997">talk</a> | <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/Special:Contributions/Mrstickman1997" class="mw-usertoollinks-contribs" title="Special:Contributions/Mrstickman1997">contribs</a>)</span> <span class="comment">(It&#039;s Experimental...)</span></div><div id="mw-revision-nav">(<a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=Portal_storm&amp;diff=prev&amp;oldid=40539" title="Portal storm">diff</a>) <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=Portal_storm&amp;direction=prev&amp;oldid=40539" title="Portal storm">← Older revision</a> | Latest revision (diff) | Newer revision → (diff)</div></div></div>
		
		
		
		<div id="jump-to-nav"></div>
		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="#mw-head">Jump to navigation</a>
		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="#p-search">Jump to search</a>
		<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><p><br />
Portal storm is a rare but extremely dangerous event. It causes <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/Nether" class="mw-redirect" title="Nether">nether</a> monsters to temporarily spawn and changes outdoor terrain. 
</p><p><b>Challenge - Portal Dependent</b> scenario creates a character in the middle of Portal Storm, far away from potential shelters.
</p><p>When portal storm starts, the game will warn about it:
</p><p><font color="magenta">You suddenly register a buzzing in your senses.  It's getting louder, and your head starts to throb.  Something is coming.</font>
</p><p>Within 2 minutes the weather will change to Early Portal Storm. After portal storm gets into full force, mini-dungeon will spawn nearby, and character will get mission **Investigate Strange Location** marking its location.
</p>
<div id="toc" class="toc"><input type="checkbox" role="button" id="toctogglecheckbox" class="toctogglecheckbox" style="display:none" /><div class="toctitle" lang="en" dir="ltr"><h2>Contents</h2><span class="toctogglespan"><label class="toctogglelabel" for="toctogglecheckbox"></label></span></div>
